name: CNN
text: On July 30, officers under the command of the Quintana Roo's State's Attorney's Office raided two buildings in Cancun and Playa del Carmen. They ultimately detained 13 people, 12 of whom were later arraigned on charges of human trafficking, among others. https://t.co/5ObRIL9ErX
